user_event
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
user_event

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
user_event -  This method calls an event on all the users online.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void user_event(mixed from,
mixed first,
mixed args ...)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^from%^RESET%^ - the person it is from
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the event
%^BOLD%^args%^RESET%^ - the arguments to the event

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/secure/simul_efun/modified_efuns.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method calls an event on all the users online.
It does not do any filtering, so it will send messages to people who
are earmuffed and ignoring or lord invisible or whatever.

.EP

